      "amount": "a few slices",
      "notes": "freshly grated or minced"
    },
    {
      "name": "scallions",
      "amount": "2-3, finely chopped",
      "notes": "raw-friendly option for added crunch"
    },
    {
      "name": "cilantro",
      "amount": "1/4 cup, finely chopped",
      "notes": "optional garnish"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Toast fennel seeds lightly in a dry skillet until fragrant and slightly golden.",
    "Combine lime juice, tamarind paste, and soy sauce in a small bowl. Stir in toasted fennel seeds.",
    "Add sliced ginger to the mixture and let it simmer for about 1 minute.",
    "Stir-fry scallions and chopped cilantro together until wilted but still crisp.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed, adding more lime juice or soy sauce if desired.",
    "Garnish with fresh herbs like cilantro or mint before serving."
